  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we did our touring, we did our learning of scout laws and scout things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only thing that we not allowed to wear uniform, scout uniform.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have scout flag.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the difference.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we kept up the scout-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] what the scout groups do.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It kept us together and kept us occupied.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And gave us a chance to-- to fill in our hearts, whatever we wouldn't have anything to do and keep up the spirits.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we thought that if we come, then we can join the real scout movement.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Few.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Few.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Tommy ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Shay, ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Gabby ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Singer ?] names come-- come to mind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was a loose, quite large group.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was basically the same group I've seen in school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They're very-- I think they were very peaceful, well-balanced, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] very normal times.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't talked about.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It wasn't-- no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Don't forget in-- in 1944, I was only 12 years old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And for a 12-year-old as long as I had my good food and my chocolate and my books and my friends and mommy and daddy around and grandpa and we can go out on the weekend to [INAUDIBLE] and up in the mountains and have a good time, I don't think we had any special concerns.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look, father closed down the business somewhere in '34 or '35.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was eight years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By the time I started to-- to know what's happening, we had a factory that was working with six, eight people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And even saw that he worked very hard.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
